    "description": "很久以前，卡拉和厄里斯和睦相处。后来，高飞龙卷风来袭，一切都变了。龙卷风席卷了全世界的羊群，只留下两个牧羊人--卡拉和艾瑞丝来拯救它们。尽管我们的牧羊人非常顽强，但在准备拯救任何人之前，他们还面临着很多挑战。你有足够的勇气应对这场冒险吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/Wishlist.gif?t=1720982926\" /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/zh__TwoPlayerCoop.png?t=1720982926\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/WorkTogether.gif?t=1720982926\" /></span><br>参与本地 2 人合作游戏，团队合作和交流是克服游戏障碍的关键。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/zh__PlaySolo.png?t=1720982926\" /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/Solo.gif?t=1720982926\" /></span><br>在制作精美的单人游戏模式中，你将扮演 Calla 或 Eris，独自应对各种独特的挑战和谜题。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/zh__SaveTheSheep.png?t=1720982926\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/SaveTheSheep.gif?t=1720982926\" /></span><br>扮演英雄，寻找并拯救村子里迷失的羊群，每只羊都非常可爱，等待救援。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/zh__PlayWithFire.png?t=1720982926\" /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/PlayWithFire.gif?t=1720982926\" /></span><br>利用工具和巧妙的思维来管理和扑灭火焰，在火光冲天的场景中进行战略导航。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/zh__FunPhysics.png?t=1720982926\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/Goofy.gif?t=1720982926\" /></span><br>有趣的物理和布偶特效让每一次挑战都变成一次欢乐的失误，让您开怀大笑。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/zh__VisualFeast.png?t=1720982926\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/Explore.gif?t=1720982926\" /></span><br>穿越艺术气息浓郁的环境，每个岛屿都能带来与谜题一样独特的视觉享受。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035520/extras/zh__KeyFeatures.png?t=1720982926\" /></span><br>- 双人本地合作游戏<br>- 单人游戏<br>- 有趣的物理和布娃娃<br>- 解开谜题，拯救危险中的绵羊！<br>- 易燃易爆的世界<br>- 排行榜<br>- 收集复活节彩蛋<br>- 支持键盘和控制器<br>- 支持超宽",
